{
  "texts": [
    "One limitation is an experimental environment.",
    "We used a crowdsourcing platform for our user study.",
    "Although user studies with crowdsourcing have been more popular, this approach has several concerns, including the demographic biases of crowd workers, the presence of lazy participants, and the control of experimental environments (task times and devices for experiments) (Ross et al., 2010).",
    "As a result, our study's participant pool might not accurately reflect the general population, and some participants might not have performed the tasks seriously.",
    "Another limitation the display timing of suggestive endings."
  ]
}